## Markdown

### Text Decoration
Text can _sort of_ be modified **whenever needed** by adding ~~just a few~~ extra `characters` to add additional emphasis to ***content***

### Links
Links work when they are either [absolute](/sample2.note) or [relative](sample2.note) or [external](https://nytimes.com)

Links can also be [Invalid](/foo/bar.note)

