```

## Equations
There are a few options for adding equations to documents. First, you can have inline math: $y = mx + b$,

You can have single-line display-style equations:

$$x = \frac{-b \pm \sqrt{b^2 - 4ac}}{2a}$$

or longer blocks of display-style equations:

$$\begin{array}{lcl}
f(x) & = & (a+b)^2 \\
& = & a^2+2ab+b^2 \\
\end{array}$$

## Diagrams
Fenced code blocks can be used for mermaid diagrams

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{Is it?}
    B -->|Yes| C[OK]
    C --> D[Rethink]
    D --> B
    B ---->|No| E[End]
```

## Shorthand Elements

### Todos
- [ ] An incomplete todo with no date stamp :sample:
- [ ] (2021-04-11) An incomplete todo created a long time ago

### Questions & Answers
None of these have dates stamped, so if you change this file via the UI and save it, they will be added
- ? What color is the sky
    + @ Blue
- ? What is the meaning of life

### Definitions
- {Shorthand} A new plain-text note taking system
